page.title: 11MY LIFE - AN ASIAN BOY 8
page.content: I go to school at 8.55. I play, I work and I eat in school. I go home at 3.35 and I go to Mosque at 5.00. I pray at Mosque then I go home at 7.15, eat and then go to bed. All that I do on week days. On Saturday and Sunday I go on journeys, always to Manchester to meet my cousin.I work at home as well and I play inside aswell as outside. I go to sleep at 9.00 but on Saturday I go to sleep at 10.30 because on Sunday I have to go nowhere. I have a bath on Sunday and I have to do my Mosque homework.
